  id: wfo_cec_tf_04
  displayName: Funding Shortage
  description: After receiving your initial investment, the student team returns
    to you with concerning news. They explain that the development costs of the missile
    system turned out to be far higher than they originally expected. According to
    them, the project cannot continue unless additional funding is secured. They
    ask you for more money to keep the project alive and finish the system.
  devNote: 
  eventNote: "\xD6\u011Frencilere yapt\u0131\u011F\u0131n ilk yat\u0131r\u0131m\u0131n
    ard\u0131ndan ekip tekrar yan\u0131na gelir ve endi\u015Fe verici bir haber verir.
    F\xFCze sisteminin geli\u015Ftirme maliyetlerinin tahmin ettiklerinden \xE7ok
    daha y\xFCksek \xE7\u0131kt\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131 s\xF6ylerler. Onlara g\xF6re
    ek finansman bulunmazsa proje devam edemeyecektir. Projeyi s\xFCrd\xFCrebilmek
    ve sistemi tamamlayabilmek i\xE7in senden daha fazla para isterler."
